# Artifact layout

**Gitignored local scratch** — entire `docs/superpowers/` tree. Never commit it.

| Subfolder | Skill / use | Naming |
|-----------|-------------|--------|
| `docs/superpowers/specs/` | `brainstorming` | `YYYY-MM-DD-<topic>-design.md` |
| `docs/superpowers/plans/` | `writing-plans`, `executing-plans` | `YYYY-MM-DD-<feature>.md` |
| `docs/superpowers/prototypes/<feature-slug>/` | `huashu-design`, wireframes, HTML variants | kebab-case folder; `.html` / `.png` inside |

Use the same `<feature-slug>` across specs, plans, and prototypes for one effort.

## Project overrides (global skills)

Global `huashu-design` defaults to `_temp/design-demos/` — **ignore that here**. Always write HTML to `docs/superpowers/prototypes/<feature-slug>/`.

## Committed truth after ship

- Architecture / flows → `docs/ai-wiki/` (+ `changelog.md`)
- UI spec → `public/vira-lata-ds.html` only
- Wiki must not depend on local spec paths for essential understanding

## `public/` rule

Shippable assets only (DS, badges, fonts, maps, manifest). No exploration HTML except `vira-lata-ds.html`. Prototype fonts: relative path e.g. `../../../../public/fonts/…`.

## Deprecated — do not use

Repo-root `_*.html`, `docs/design/`, `docs/wireframes/`, `_temp/`. Throwaway **code** prototypes (`prototype` skill) live next to target modules in `src/` with clear naming.

## UI pipeline

`huashu-design` → `docs/superpowers/prototypes/<feature-slug>/` → user locks → `frontend-design` in `src/` + update `vira-lata-ds.html`.

Full skill matrix → `.claude/context/skill-routing.md` · canonical copy in `CLAUDE.md` § Artifact layout.
